n:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pod 뿐만 아니라 모든 Object에 달 수 있는데, 주로 Pod에서 가장 많이 사용됨</li>\n<li>목적에 따라 Object들을 분류하고 분류된 Object들만 따로 골라서 연결하기 위함</li>\n<li>Key와 Value로 이루어짐</li>\n<li>같은 라벨을 가진 Pod들끼리 서비스로 묶어 접속 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">apiVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> v1\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">kind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Pod\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pod<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">labels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> web\n\t\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">lo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> dev\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">containers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> container\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ugaemi/init</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">apiVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> v1\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">kind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Service\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> svc<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">selector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> web\n\t<span class=\"token key atrule\">ports</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">port</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"node-schedule\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#node-schedule\" aria-label=\"node schedule permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#node-schedule\" aria-label=\"node schedule permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Node Schedule</h3>\n<ul>\n<li